window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>As his power grows, so do the threats.</b></p> <p>Thanks to the unconditional love and support from the women in his life, Ward Moreno has recovered the memories he lost due to SigNet’s brutal experimentation. Yet before he and his flock can celebrate, Doctor Hano attacks while seeking a new subject for his experiments: Tara Fiore.</p> <p>Ward isn’t about to let Hano take her. To stop the mad doctor, he’ll brave a deadly jungle, an ancient temple, and an army of mechanized opponents. As strong as he is now, it’ll still be a tough fight.</p> <p>But some help from an old ally turned enemy might just even the odds.</p>"; 
